    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 瞭解行銷的角色<br>2. 行銷資訊與行銷研究<br>3. 掌握市場機會<br>4. 塑造產品價值<br>5. 促進產品流通<br>6. 傳達產品價值<br>7. 行銷執行與控制",
        "en": "1. Introduction to marketing<br>2. Marketing information system and marketing research<br>3. Identifying market opportunity<br>4. Creating the value of product<br>5. Product promotion<br>6. Delivering product value<br>7. Marketing control"
